rows.label: bf10200100_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Wha...?

rows.label: bf10200100_0020
rows.name: Gramps-!

rows.label: bf10200100_0030
rows.name: This place...

rows.label: bf10200100_0040
rows.name: What's the point of all this...

rows.label: bf10200100_0050
rows.name: Gramps?

rows.label: bf10200100_0060
rows.name: What purpose do we have?

rows.label: bf10200100_0070
rows.name:
We are born as Blades,
then fall into slumber,

rows.label: bf10200100_0080
rows.name: spending an unimaginably long time,

rows.label: bf10200100_0090
rows.name:
then we become Divine Beasts,
and spend another eternity,

rows.label: bf10200100_0100
rows.name: until finally fading away to nothing.

rows.label: bf10200100_0110
rows.name: Have you ever thought about it?

rows.label: bf10200100_0120
rows.name:
What it means to exist for an
eternity without any clear purpose?

rows.label: bf10200100_0130
rows.name: That's...

rows.label: bf10200100_0140
rows.name: Humans have it good...

rows.label: bf10200100_0150
rows.name: Living for only a short time,

rows.label: bf10200100_0160
rows.name:
thinking only about immediate concerns...
How much simpler it must be.

rows.label: bf10200100_0170
rows.name: I envy you all...

rows.label: bf10200100_0180
rows.name: Tell me, Rex.

rows.label: bf10200100_0190
rows.name: What should I do?

rows.label: bf10200100_0200
rows.name:
Is it enough just to drift across
the sea with you riding on my back?

rows.label: bf10200100_0210
rows.name: Is that my entire purpose?

rows.label: bf10200100_0220
rows.name:
I-I don't know. How am I
supposed to answer that?

rows.label: bf10200100_0230
rows.name: Why are you asking me this?!

rows.label: bf10200100_0240
rows.name:
You're not making sense...
Everyone's acting so weird!
